The ultimate Dota movie collection
Tout regarder

Discover a ton of awesome animated movies & SFM creators! I started curating a playlist because I was getting sick of freebooters & reuploaders stealing and monetizing other people's hard work. And I thought, if I could help fans find out who actually makes movies, then it will not only help against thieves, but it will also benefit everyone. While this will mostly contain SFM videos, expect a few outliers! This playlist is automatically sorted by date published; newer videos are at the top. If you are a Dota movie creator I invite you to showcase this playlist, whether it's in video descriptions or directly on your channel (add section, playlist url) If you have any suggestions for movies to add here, tweet at @MaxOfS2D (or if you have a huge list, shoot me an e-mail)
